#################################################
#  Conways game of life in a binary matrix in C #
#  for fun and games - Alfred Laderoute 2021    #
#################################################


Example usage

./a.out 15 15 1500

(Note this may take a few attempts to get a working game)

This will run a simulation of a 15 by 15 grid of max 1500 iterations.

